# Perfect Torture

Thoughts on how technology could be used for torture.

Link: https://humanit.home.blog/2024/01/15/perfect-tech-perfect-torture/

- Technology could be used to extract a person's thoughts. Privacy could become impossible.
- Fear and pain could be stimulated in a person's mind, and could go on indefinitely. (AI could play a role in finding the "optimal" way to do this.)
- New torture methods when combined with anti-aging tech could create hell.
- There is fear about an AI going rogue and doing this, but there's no reason to believe humans wouldn't just do this to each other.
- Someone will probably come up with it eventually...
